Package: SCRAT
Type: Package
Title: SCRAT: Single-Cell Regulome Analysis Tool
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2016-1-18
Author: Zhicheng Ji, Weiqiang Zhou, Hongkai Ji
Maintainer: Zhicheng Ji <zji4@jhu.edu>
Description: SCRAT provides essential tools for users to read in single-cell
    regolome data (ChIP-seq, ATAC-seq, DNase-seq) and summarize into different types
    of features. It also allows users to visualize the features, cluster samples and
    identify key features.
License: GPL(>=2)
Imports:
    shiny,
    GenomicAlignments,
    ggplot2,
    reshape2,
    pheatmap,
    scatterD3,
    d3heatmap
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests:
    knitr,
    SCRATdatahg19,
    SCRATdatahg38,
    SCRATdatamm9,
    SCRATdatamm10
Depends:
    R(>= 2.10.0)
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
